    "body" : "<p>No need to add new plugin in pom.xml. Just run this command </p>\n\n<pre><code>mvn org.codehaus.mojo:exec-maven-plugin:1.5.0:java -Dexec.mainClass=\"com.example.Main\" | grep -Ev '(^\\[|Download\\w+:)' \n</code></pre>\n\n<p>See the <a href=\"http://www.mojohaus.org/exec-maven-plugin/usage.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\" title=\"exec usage\">maven exec plugin</a> for more usage.</p>\n"
