    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<h2>1. Edit POM.xml</h2>\n<p>Add the following property in <code>pom.xml</code>. Make sure you use the fully qualified class name (i.e. with package name) which contains the <code>main</code> method:</p>\n<pre><code>    &lt;properties&gt;\n      &lt;exec.mainClass&gt;fully-qualified-class-name&lt;/exec.mainClass&gt;\n    &lt;/properties&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<h2>2. Run Command</h2>\n<p>Now from the terminal, trigger the following command:</p>\n<pre><code>mvn clean compile exec:java\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong> You can pass further arguments via <code>-Dexec.args=&quot;xxx&quot;</code> flag.</p>\n"
  } ],
